---
title: Golden Coconut Fish Curry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Embark on a culinary journey with our with our golden curry, a harmonious blend of tender white fish bathed in a rich coconutty sauce. With pops of carrot and green beans throughout, this exotic dish promises a perfect balance of freshness and creaminess.
